## Outcome

Introduce the trusted process runtime core outside the V1 composition SDK: process manager, JSON-RPC stdio protocol, lifecycle contracts, runtime overlays, route-scoped blockers, and result attachment.

## Execution Posture

Keep process state namespaced under process-family contracts. Processes return data-only refs and provenance; they never gain timeline mutation rights.

