- Process lifecycle is not a material status and not a V1 composition target.
- Process task results map into M3a material statuses only through returned artifacts/materials.
- Every task-scoped message includes task/process/operation correlation.
- Payloads exceeding implementation limits return artifact locators, not inline blobs.
